record.comment_content: Hi, this is a comment. To get started with moderating, editing, and deleting comments, please visit the Comments screen in the dashboard. Commenter avatars come from Gravatar.
Simple and effective design. One of my favorites.
Wonderful quality, and an awesome design. WooThemes ftw!

This t-shirt is awesome! Would recommend to everyone!

I'm ordering mine next week
Nice T-shirt, I got one in black. Goes with anything!
Very comfortable shirt, and I love the graphic!
Great T-shirt quality, Great Design and Great Service.
The ninja silhouette is one of my favorite designs. This is a great product.
This will go great with my Hoodie that I ordered a few weeks ago.
Love this shirt! The ninja near and dear to my heart. <3
Another great quality product that anyone who see's me wearing has asked where to purchase one of their own.
This hoodie gets me lots of looks while out in public, I got the blue one and it's awesome. Not sure if people are looking at my hoodie only, or also at my rocking bod.
Ship it!
This hoodie is great for those chilly winter days. I love the WooNinja!
Perfect for the lady Ninja in your life!
Perfect when you're sat at your computer, waiting for the next batch of Woo Goodies to be released. The Patient Ninja is Patient.
The most comfortable hoodie I have ever owned!

This is my favorite hoodie!

If only it came in red as well!
I bought this thinking it was a nice green color, apparently it GREY! I'm color blind so I don't care but my girlfriend says grey makes me look fat
I love grey hoodies! This is perfect with my grey Ninja shirt, when I get cold I throw this on and I can still be a Ninja.
Perfect Hoodie for a Ninja!
I have lots of hoodies, but none is as cool as this one!
I love hoodies, and ninjas, so what could be better than a ninja hoodie? Not much, if you ask me!
This is the most bombastic hoodie in this shop, it's soft and has the sly WooThemes ninja on it. Why wouldn't you buy this?
This only gets 1 star because I don't have this yet. I want it now!
The best hoodie ever!
I like the logo but not the color.
Three letters, one word: WOO!
Really happy with this print. The colors are great, and the paper quality is good too.
You only get the picture, not the person holding it, something they don't mention in the description, now I've got to find my own person
This is my favorite poster. In fact, I've ordered 5 of them!
This is a fantastic quality print and is happily hanging framed on my wall now.
I thought I was buying a man holding a poster, but when it arrived it was just the poster. Cool poster though, so I'll give it 3 stars!
I didn't expect this poster to arrive folded. Now there are lines on the poster and one sad Ninja.
He really is the cutest little man. Swoooon!
Wonderful collection of WooThemes classics! A must buy for all Woo fans.
This album gets a bit boring after you've listened to it more than once. Worth that first listen though.
The most influential album of the last 25 years? This just might be it.
Some rad tunes on this album!
This album proves why The Woo are the best band ever. Best music ever!
Can’t wait to start mixin’ with this one! Irba-irr-Up-up-up-up-date your theme!
